list.item:
Cables were cleared, as revised, on the following: 

—to Saigon and Phnom Penh on Mekong River escort;

—to Saigon on Congressional considerations involved in Mekong
                                escort;

—To Phnom Penh, Saigon and CINCPAC on training assistance for [less than 1 line not declassified];

—to Saigon and Phnom Penh on GVN
                                material support to [less than 1 line not
                                    declassified];

—to Phnom Penh, Saigon and [less than 1 line not
                                    declassified].
